@page "/"

<PageTitle>About Spreadsheet</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <h1>Welcome to Our Spreadsheet Application</h1>
    <p>
        This application is a Spreadsheet that allows you to keep track of your data.
    </p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Interactive Grid:</b> Easily inputdata in a grid format. Each cell can contain numbers, text, or formulas.</li>
        <li><b>Formulas:</b> Input formulas starting with <code>=</code> to perform calculations across cells.</li>
        <li><b>Files:</b> Save and load your spreadsheets to continue where you left off. All data is stored in JSON format.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Additional Feature: Dark Mode Toggle</h2>
    <p>
        Our Spreadsheet includes an <b>Additional Feature</b> that lets you switch between Light Mode and Dark Mode with a simple button click.
    </p>
    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <p>
       Click on the Spreadsheet page on the left to start making your own spreadsheet.
    </p>
    <h2>Authors</h2>
    <p>
        Minh Quoc Vo and Ryan Boardman
    </p>
</div>

